{"type":null,"faqId":49826,"title":"华为智能手表_手表支持音乐播放吗？如何使用？","answer":"<body style=\"clear:both; padding-left:10px; padding-top:5px; padding-right:5px; padding-bottom:5px\"><div id=\"body28309076\"><p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329155__p3652259519256\">支持</p><p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329155__p2902394319215\"><strong id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329155__b5988890119215\">享受手机音乐：</strong></p><p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329155__p212919719215\">手表和手机正常连接后，可以控制手机音乐的播放，如切换歌曲、调节音量。</p><p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329155__p3913555719147\">通过安卓手机自带播放器、华为音乐、网易云音乐等app播放音乐，可以使用手表切换歌曲、调节音量。</p><div class=\"note\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329155__note6139928319158\"><img src=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/7c506_xdqzt.gif\"><span class=\"notetitle\"> 说明： </span><div class=\"notebody\"><p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329155__p406899911921\">手机使用酷狗音乐、虾米音乐、百度音乐app播放时，手表侧不会出现控制卡片。</p></div></div><p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329155__p1203716219219\"><strong id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329155__b4122560019219\">享受离线音乐：</strong></p><p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329155__p593723821917\">手表支持蓝牙音乐播放，方便用户在走路、跑步、运动等不方便携带手机时享受离线音乐。您可以按照以下方式播放蓝牙音乐：</p><ol id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329155__ol1940599419533\"><li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329155__li3343213619533\">在安卓手机、平板设备中下载、安装WearADay中国版app。</li><li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329155__li3647849919533\">打开WearADay中国版，将手机中的音乐同步到手表中。</li><li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329155__li2571389619533\">在手表<strong id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329155__b6180854519533\">设置 &gt; 蓝牙设备</strong>中查找并连接蓝牙耳机。</li><li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329155__li4179886419533\">在手表中点击音乐开始播放，通过蓝牙耳机收听。</li></ol><div class=\"note\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329155__note2929942419546\"><img src=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/7c506_xdqzt.gif\"><span class=\"notetitle\"> 说明： </span><div class=\"notebody\"><p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329155__p5514962819552\">离线音乐是通过蓝牙支持的，必须保证手机在十米以内，在室外跑步时也得带着手机在身边。</p></div></div></div><div><div class=\"familylinks\"></div></div></body>","faqTypeId":615,"faqType":"拍照与多媒体","useful":2,"unUseful":4,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"zh-cn_topic_0022329155","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Photo-Media","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1448615424000,"seriesProductName":"Mercury-G00,Mercury-G01,Mercury-G10","visitedTimes":264,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"音乐，播放","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}